reased_by_1_5_times" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brave_group_raises_1_99_billion_yen_in_new_funding_the_number_of_affiliated_vtuber_has_increased_by_1_5_times.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brave_group_raises_1_99_billion_yen_in_new_funding_the_number_of_affiliated_vtuber_has_increased_by_1_5_times.jpg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brave_group_raises_1_99_billion_yen_in_new_funding_the_number_of_affiliated_vtuber_has_increased_by_1_5_times.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-99349"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © Brave group Inc.</figcaption></figure><p>本次融资由Simplex Capital Investment Co., Ltd.、东京理科大学Innovation Capital Co., Ltd.、Money Forward Venture Partners Co., Ltd.（HIRAC FUND No.2 Investment Business Limited Liability Association）领投， Revamp Co., Ltd. 共有五家公司以及 Adways Ventures 担任承销商。</p><p> Adways Ventures 是 Adways Inc. 的子公司，Adways Inc. 是 774 Inc. 的母公司，774 Inc. 运营着 VTuber 办公室 Nanashinku。</p><p>凭借本次融资，Brave集团累计融资金额达到50.3亿日元。</p><p>通过子公司，该公司是VTuber集团<strong>巴士流行！</strong> 、 <strong>RIOT MUSIC</strong> 、 <strong>Palette Project</strong> 、 <strong>V4Mirai</strong> 、 <strong>globie</strong>等</p><p></p><div class="celpz64e6d93b99e98" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
